<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得赶到邦恩太太家。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人抢劫了客人的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来。我要给爸妈打电话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大声对朋友们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别去太久了。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“音乐会马上就要开始了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过一会儿，罗西飞上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”玛拉大声说，“是火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了邦恩太太家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦恩太太看上去很难过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在玫瑰丛里爬来爬去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在做园艺工作吗， 侦探先生？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！火箭女孩儿。”史密斯侦探假装大笑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！刺扎到我了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起来，举起笔记本。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把这个掉在玫瑰丛里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探转向邦恩太太。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。刚才您说到哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦恩太太叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说到了我的客人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你想跟他们谈的话，他们都还在这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>服务人员和四重奏乐团也在。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四重奏乐团？”史密斯侦探扬起一边的眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“管弦乐四重奏乐团。”邦恩太太说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我请了四个音乐家在派对上表演。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抢劫以前发生过什么事吗？”罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么可疑的地方吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦恩太太耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真奇怪，我竟然什么都不记得了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前一分钟，我们还在享受美好的时光，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后一分钟，每个人的钱包都不见了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有我们的珠宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探做了一些笔记。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要跟每个人都谈谈，邦恩太太。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到了音乐家。“从他们开始吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人看到可疑的事情了吗？”罗西问音乐家们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”大提琴家说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过我希望你能找到罪犯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个小偷偷走了我的手表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着自己的大提琴，叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“幸好我还有它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的红宝石耳环不见了！”一位小提琴家说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下！”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们只有三个人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邦恩太太说你们是四重奏乐团。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊！”第三个音乐家说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“瓦奥莱特去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“瓦奥莱特•夏普。”大提琴家说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是我们另外一位小提琴家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”罗西说，“有人偷了客人的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在瓦奥莱特又不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>的确很可疑啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可能！”小提琴家说，“瓦奥莱特才不是小偷呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是个很有才的音乐家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，美罗城交响乐团还邀请她去面试呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让人印象深刻啊。”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正在这时，他的手机响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？天啊！我马上就过去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挂了电话，看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才又发生了一起抢劫案，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次是在美罗城购物中心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>